_header: A bird in cage fast locked with gold
_description: On desire for liberty — two cross-rhymed quatrains

OxfLinLat141.First Lines:
A byrd in cage fast locked with goldeThough shee be fedde most
                    dayntily…
OxfLinLat141.Last Lines:
…Is thraldome like to libertyewill thou exchaung that good for
                    ill
